+# Fresh verifier problems: MVP-02-admin-ui-status-view-001
+
+Verdict: `FAIL`
+Verified at: 2026-05-11T14:53:49Z
+
+This verifier covers only `MVP-02-admin-ui-status-view-001`. It does not close full `MVP-02.04`, full `MVP-02` or the MVP stage.
+
+## Blocking Gaps
+
+1. Russian operator copy is not fully proven.
+   - Evidence: [admin-code-status-screen.tsx](/Users/elena/cursor/FinPulse/apps/admin/components/admin-code-status-screen.tsx:44) renders `data.cohortStatus` directly.
+   - Screenshot evidence shows `500 · PLANNED` under `План / статус` in both desktop and mobile success states.
+   - This contradicts AC-4 and the explicit UI/operator copy Russian constraint.
+   - Minimal fix: render Russian labels for cohort status values (`PLANNED`, `ACTIVE`, `CLOSED`) and refresh admin typecheck/test/build plus screenshot evidence.
+
+2. Current verifier `git diff --check` fails.
+   - Evidence: [.agent/stages/mvp/evidence.md](/Users/elena/cursor/FinPulse/.agent/stages/mvp/evidence.md:3) contains trailing whitespace.
+   - Raw ref: `.agent/stages/mvp/raw/stage-verifier-mvp-02-admin-ui-status-view-001-git-diff-check-20260511.txt`.
+   - Minimal fix: remove the trailing whitespace, rerun `git diff --check` and refresh the raw evidence.
+
+## Proven Or Credible
+
+- `pnpm --filter @finrhythm/admin typecheck`: PASS.
+- `pnpm --filter @finrhythm/admin test`: PASS.
+- `make verify`: PASS with explicit Homebrew JDK 21 `JAVA_HOME/PATH`.
+- `make test-unit`: PASS with explicit Homebrew JDK 21 `JAVA_HOME/PATH`.
+- `make build`: PASS with explicit Homebrew JDK 21 `JAVA_HOME/PATH`.
+- Backend/API/schema stayed out of this UI slice; `git diff -- apps/api` is empty.
+- `packages/api-client` remains no-op with only `.gitkeep`.
+- Guardrail scan found no raw invite-code value pattern, lookup hash, activation subject ref, employee contact fields, diagnostics, weak zones, financial data or customer brand in managed admin source/fixture.
+- Existing builder browser smoke using installed system Google Chrome produced desktop/mobile success plus empty/error/loading PNGs; verifier inspected the success screenshots.
+
+## Non-Blocking Notes
+
+- A verifier rerun of Playwright smoke against `next start` failed because system Chrome aborted at launch before navigation. This is recorded as verifier raw evidence and is not the blocking reason for this FAIL.
+- One verifier Maven-wrapper precheck without exported `JAVA_HOME` failed via the macOS Java stub; the rerun with explicit Homebrew JDK 21 passed.
+- The mobile builder screenshot contains a Next dev indicator overlay; this verifier did not treat it as a blocker because the existing smoke assertions and PNG files are otherwise present, but refreshed screenshots after the copy fix should avoid dev overlays if possible.
+- Harness verification after writing the current verdict alias still returns `FAIL` because `status.json.latest_verified_sprint_contract_id` correctly remains `MVP-02-admin-code-status-view-001` while this UI sprint is non-pass.
+
+## Human Gates Still Open
+
+- Legal/privacy wording: `WAITING_HUMAN`.
+- Consent copy: `WAITING_HUMAN`.
+- Real employee/customer data processing: `WAITING_HUMAN`.
+- Customer-specific reporting boundaries: `WAITING_HUMAN`.
+- Admin auth/role/audit policy for production use: `WAITING_HUMAN`.
